p_c-p)}^{-\\gamma}$, with\n$\\gamma \\simeq 1.18, 1.11, 1.05$ in infinite-dimension (rest of the $N-1$\nneighboring restaurants), three-dimension ($6$ neighbors) and two-dimension\n($4$ neighbors) respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 May 2019 17:49:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Aug 2019 02:39:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 14 Feb 2020 14:24:24 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2020 09:41:12 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2020 18:07:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-10"}
