 the phonon frequencies are related to\nthe 2D dielectric functions or susceptibilities. The explicit expressions are\napplied to calculate various dynamical properties when knowing three\nfirst-principles calculated parameters, and the ionic EP and LFEs are studied\nthoroughly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 May 2019 06:00:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-03"}
