 surface\nproperties of the neutron $^{3}P_{2}$ superfluid found in this paper may\nprovide us useful information to study neutron stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 May 2019 15:11:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Mar 2020 07:56:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-09"}
